09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>URL 파라미터(URL Parameter)</h3>\n<p>주소 경로에 유동적인 값을 넣는 형태로서, id나 이름 등을 사용하여 특정 <strong>데이터를 조회</strong>할 때 사용한다.  </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://comic.naver.com/webtoon/weekday\">https://comic.naver.com/webtoon/weekday</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"쿼리-스트링query-string\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BF%BC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EB%A7%81query-string\" aria-label=\"쿼리 스트링query string permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>쿼리 스트링(Query String)</h3>\n<p>주소 뒷 부분에 <strong><code class=\"language-text\">?</code></strong> 문자열 이후 key=value로 값을 정의하여 <strong><code class=\"language-text\">&amp;</code></strong>로 구분하는 형태로서, 키워드 검색 등 데이터 조회에 필요한 <strong>옵션 전달</strong>할 때 사용한다.  </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://comic.naver.com/webtoon/weekdayList?week=mon&#x26;order=User&#x26;view=image\">https://comic.naver.com/webtoon/weekdayList?week=mon&#x26;order=User&#x26;view=image</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><br><br>  </p>\n<p><strong>reference</strong><br>\n👉 <a href=\"https://velog.io/@velopert/react-router-v6-tutorial\">https://velog.io/@velopert/react-router-v6-tutorial</a><br>\n👉 <a href=\"https://velog.io/@haesoohaesoo/useParams-useLocation-useNavigate\">https://velog.io/@haesoohaesoo/useParams-useLocation-useNavigate</a></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"September 27, 2022","title":"UMC React Study 3주차","categories":"UMC","author":"JSH99","emoji":"🛫️"},"fields":{"slug":"/UMC/React_W3/"}},"prev":null,"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://www.jsh99.com","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"JSH99/JSH99.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/UMC/React_W4/","nextSlug":"/UMC/React_W3/","prevSlug":""}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","2938748437"]}